## 3. Supabase — 3 clients distincts

| Fichier | Usage | Sync/Async |
|---------|-------|------------|
| `lib/supabase/server.ts` | Server Components + Server Actions | **async** (`await cookies()`) |
| `lib/supabase/client.ts` | Client Components uniquement | sync |
| `lib/supabase/admin.ts` | Opérations admin (bypass RLS) | sync, **serveur uniquement** |

